query:
SELECT cp.name, cp.nameAr, COUNT(q.id) as question_count 
FROM cultural_packs cp 
LEFT JOIN questions q ON cp.id = q.cultural_pack_id 
GROUP BY cp.id, cp.name, cp.nameAr 
ORDER BY cp.id
